Hydrogen
========

Created:      2022-08-23
Home page:    <https://metacpan.org/release/Hydrogen>
Bug tracker:  <https://github.com/tobyink/p5-hydrogen/issues>
Maintainer:   Toby Inkster (TOBYINK) <tobyink@cpan.org>

0.021000	2025-07-14

 - Added: Hydrogen::Autobox.
 - Updated: Rebuild with latest version of Sub::HandlesVia.

0.020000	2023-03-04

 [ Documentation ]
 - Copyright 2023.
 - Include String::Util in SEE ALSO.
 - Mention that Lexical::Sub enables lexical imports on older Perls.

 [ Test Suite ]
 - Rename a bunch of test files.

 [ Packaging ]
 - Switch to X.YYYZZZ version numbers.

0.018	2023-03-04

 - Updated: Rebuild with Sub::HandlesVia 0.046.

0.017	2022-10-21

 - Updated: Rebuild with Sub::HandlesVia 0.038.

0.016	2022-09-28

 [ Packaging ]
 - Require Exporter::Tiny 1.004001+.

 [ Other ]
 - Updated: Rebuild with latest Sub::HandlesVia.

0.015	2022-08-27

 [ Documentation ]
 - Remove SYNOPSIS example that didn't work.

0.014	2022-08-27

 [ Documentation ]
 - Add a RATIONALE section.
 - Improve SYNOPSIS.

 [ Other ]
 - Generate some slightly more efficient mutator functions for strings,
   arrays, and hashes.

0.013	2022-08-27

 - Updated: Use Exporter::Shiny 1.004000 so that Hydrogen can do lexical
   exports on Perl 5.37.2+.

0.012	2022-08-26

 - Updated: Rebuild with latest Sub::HandlesVia.

0.011	2022-08-26

 [ Bug Fixes ]
 - Perl 5.8.x doesn't support re::is_regexp(), so provide a polyfill for a
   few functions in Hydrogen::String and Hydrogen::Topic::String which
   require it.

 [ Documentation ]
 - Document distribution dependencies.

 [ Test Suite ]
 - Rewrite test suite to use Test2::V0.

 [ Other ]
 - Support Perl as old as 5.8.1.

0.010	2022-08-26

 [ Documentation ]
 - Fix missing linebreak before '=head1 BUGS' in pod.

0.009	2022-08-26

 [ Documentation ]
 - Minor pod improvements.

 [ Test Suite ]
 - Minor improvements.

 [ Other ]
 - Minor formatting changes.

0.008	2022-08-25

 [ Documentation ]
 - Document Hydrogen.pm's own exported functions.
 - Give an example of topicalized function usage in Hydrogen.pm SYNOPSIS.
 - Improve the module listing in Hydrogen.pm.

0.007	2022-08-25

 - Added: Hydrogen::Topic::* modules.
 - Some improved error messages.

